    "The left-hand panel illustrates the case of equal capital and labor endowments, K = L = 1, and modest complementarity with an elasticity of substitution σ = 0.5 between the two.",
    "As long as the economy is in the scarcelabor region (Region 1), output is a strictly monotonic function of automation."
